manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Power Your Dream PC with Our Elite 850W PSU - 80 PLUS Gold Certified Performance and Reliability in One Unit Uneec Fully-Modular 750W G series is designed to power the most demanding setups, it's perfect for gaming rigs, creative workstations, and any PC that requires robust and steady power. Enjoy a seamless experience with our top-tier PSU that combines efficiency with unmatched power.

Maximize Your Energy Efficiency Proven Performance with Superior Energy Efficiency With 80 PLUS Gold certification, these platinum power supplies deliver high efficiency of up to 90%, reducing your energy costs and ensuring reliable and stable power delivery. Our PSU is rigorously tested and verified, promising not just superior energy savings but also peace of mind, thanks to its robust protection features and compatibility with a wide range of setups.
Fully Modular Cable Design The fully modular cable design allows use of only the cables you need for reduced system clutter and improved air flow.

Advanced Features for Peak Performance 80 Plus Gold efficiency It provides ultra-high power efficiency of at least 90% at 50% load, reducing electricity costs and less heat generation, which is beneficial for system stability and longevity. Silm Silent Fan The hydraulic bearing fan ensures quiet operation while effectively dissipating heat, keeping performance smooth and steady even under heavy loads. Comprehensive Protection Over Current/Voltage/Power/Temperature Protection, Under Voltage Protection, and Short Circuit Protection provide maximum safety to your critical system components.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good replacement for what I had
reviews.reviewText: Old power supply in the computer decided to stop working, so I needed a replacement. As the one I had in there was a modular power supply, I wanted as close to the exact replacement as I could get. I found this one to be the best deal, still a little pricey in my mind, but it works for what I needed. Powered up right away and stayed on (That was the main focus) Happy with the choice.
